    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一款融合了跑酷和策略炒股的轻度肉鸽卡牌游戏。可体验从炒股萌新到最强股神的成功之路！轻松休闲还是刺激烧脑？任你选择！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>刺激爽快的跑酷收集体验！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0e0d7f75bec8c702fbcb30922f718001.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0e0d7f75bec8c702fbcb30922f718001.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/0e0d7f75bec8c702fbcb30922f718001.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现金、道具、股票买卖、障碍物、涨跌门...近百种不同物品出现在一条跑道上，每次触碰都是惊喜与收获。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当收集足够数量稀有金属，将开启一场愉悦而动听的结算体验，享受金钱源源不断收入囊中的快感！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富多样的卡牌策略！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/a770200a4a1b1af542a425029911de88.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/a770200a4a1b1af542a425029911de88.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/a770200a4a1b1af542a425029911de88.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经济类、可成长类、强力递减类、特殊效果类...六十余张功能各异卡牌，搭建你的独特专属卡组！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌持续更新中~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>猝不及防的突发事件！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/9a5c22a1eb99cd9d7b31c7fcbf702ac3.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/9a5c22a1eb99cd9d7b31c7fcbf702ac3.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/9a5c22a1eb99cd9d7b31c7fcbf702ac3.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将遭遇五十场突发事件，他们将深深影响股票价格。仔细阅读，财富的秘密就隐藏在其中！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种难度的Boss关卡等你挑战！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6bf3dc573bae3153bad902174046af42.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6bf3dc573bae3153bad902174046af42.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/6bf3dc573bae3153bad902174046af42.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >十二位希腊主神对应十二项高难度挑战关卡，神并非无私无欲，内心深处阴暗反映最真实的“神”！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>种类繁多的道具！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/12a0d1ffbda73b0e83f7b29d10fd364f.poster.avif?t=1734415282\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/12a0d1ffbda73b0e83f7b29d10fd364f.webm?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085020/extras/12a0d1ffbda73b0e83f7b29d10fd364f.mp4?t=1734415282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超大范围吸取、飞速横向移动、涨跌反转...趣味道具系统让跑酷更加有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快来加入体验吧~</strong></p>",
